{"tid":1595661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【英國戰線】登記做英國選民！依家喺、即將去、曾經住過英國嘅，全部同我入晒嚟！","createTime":"2019-09-26T07:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T23:42:36.000Z","uid":27579,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"f412bb4b5b472cd093300a4b5cc4616efccc1f3b","tid":1595661,"uid":27579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:16:43.000Z","msg":"【頭盔：幫fd 子post，我自己係英聯邦國籍都登記左了，大家唔好猶疑，登記左先！】 <br />\n<br />\n我哋係一群喺英國住咗幾年嘅香港人。<br />\n<br />\n我哋之前大家寫信畀各區國會議員，動之以情，但唔少回應都只係啲行貨。點解會咁？因為佢除咗普世價值之外，實在冇動力去幫香港人。<br />\n<br />\n我哋諗，點樣可以說之以利，令啲政界人物覺得幫我哋香港人唔單止係道理，亦都有佢着數？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">選票!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n英國今年內（11、12月）好大機會提前大選。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只要你現居英國，無論係英國公民、BNO、或英聯邦國家嘅國民，無論你持有咩visa都好，都可以登記做英國選民。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你即將過嚟讀書、working holiday，嚟緊九月尾/十月頭到埗，你應該趕得切登記做英國選民。<br />\n<br />\n如果你係英國公民，而又曾經喺英國住過，只要離英未夠15年，你可以登記喺海外郵寄投票。<br />\n<br />\n立即登記(只需要5分鐘): <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/register-to-vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fregister-to-vote&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=98ddd5dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/register-to-vote</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EJwR4cC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEJwR4cC.png&h=b90f8464&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KFRnrq1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKFRnrq1.png&h=b52b96d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋希望幫助所有合資格嘅香港手足，盡快登記做選民。其實登記咗唔單止可以幫香港，之後喺英國申請信用咭，呢邊啲銀行都係用選民登記冊做background check，所以絕對應該做，值得做，快啲做。<br />\n<br />\n差你一個，真係好多！！！！<br />\n<br />\n我哋分析過2017大選結果。英國選情仲激烈過香港區議會。<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">蘇格蘭NE Fife選區，即係 St Andrew's 大學所在地， 係2票定勝負！而最多香港人嘅倫敦，其中Imperial College所在嘅Kensington選區，工黨只係贏保守黨20票！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果遇上阻滯、遇上問題，請入嚟我哋嘅Telegram group：<a href=\"http://t.me/UKVoterAction4HK。我哋會盡力幫你解決。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUKVoterAction4HK%E3%80%82%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E6%9C%83%E7%9B%A1%E5%8A%9B%E5%B9%AB%E4%BD%A0%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E3%80%82&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=115eb14a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/UKVoterAction4HK。我哋會盡力幫你解決。</a><br />\n<br />\n未來行動：<br />\n● 我哋會整理英國各城市爭持激烈嘅選區(搖擺選區 / marginal seats)list。即將搬嚟英國，又未落戶嘅巴絲可以考慮下住係啲marginal seats，啲候選人會比較重視開拓新票源。<br />\n● 整電郵生成器，幫大家聯絡啲候選人；<br />\n● 喺啲香港同路人比較多，或者各黨爭持激烈嘅選區，組織大家約見候選人(面對面見，等佢哋有印象！佢哋競選都係要票，唔使怕醜)；<br />\n● 整理候選人對香港議題嘅立場/政綱，俾大家投票時參考。<br />\n<br />\n希望可以借助嚟緊選舉嘅契機，去engage呢邊嘅選舉政治，促使啲國會議員為香港發聲。<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<br />\nDemocracy for Hong Kong - Electoral Action Group 選舉行動組 (D4HK-EAG) <br />\n謹啟<br />\n<br />\nP.S.立即登記(只需要5分鐘): <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/register-to-vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fregister-to-vote&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=98ddd5dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/register-to-vote</a> <br />\n<br />\nP.P.S. D4HK Facebook 原post：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1572411313051960/posts/2152331705059915/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1572411313051960%2Fposts%2F2152331705059915%2F&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=798feeb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1572411313051960/posts/2152331705059915/</a>"},{"pid":"65ea3357fdc5cc4e1f6a960025d89b12067837ce","tid":1595661,"uid":278456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:26:06.000Z","msg":"英國巴絲辛苦哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac0e73076a92801ebe3ccdce8c38d5d36f98fdf","tid":1595661,"uid":188020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:26:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407c441057a9377c821cf4fdbf6a53f4643382a3","tid":1595661,"uid":27579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:26:18.000Z","msg":"推到有英國巴絲入黎！"},{"pid":"aacc404b088a69f534da4898d2812da09496f370","tid":1595661,"uid":27725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:28:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ccb72476971f95a0bcd4d96037dd86dcdbf3c39","tid":1595661,"uid":267721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:46:26.000Z","msg":"仲追POST，快啲登記啦。我啱啱登記咗，當區國會議員即刻寫信畀我跪票🙇🏼&zwj;♀️🙇🏿&zwj;♂️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️！"},{"pid":"e73461e43cb52d70f0f97c854f006535eb3e9ce1","tid":1595661,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:50:02.000Z","msg":"BNO 都得？<br />\n有冇source?"},{"pid":"c83207ed2667389f6639cc585af8430078eeb2a0","tid":1595661,"uid":27579,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e73461e43cb52d70f0f97c854f006535eb3e9ce1","tid":1595661,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:50:02.000Z","msg":"BNO 都得？<br />\n有冇source?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:02:10.000Z","msg":"之前SCMP 有個報導有講，可見<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/2157756/what-british-national-overseas-passport-and-what-holder\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Famp.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F2157756%2Fwhat-british-national-overseas-passport-and-what-holder&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=16bf95e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/2157756/what-british-national-overseas-passport-and-what-holder</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，係英國政府個網都有講，BN(O) 本身都係一種nationality，以我嘅理解。即係BN(O) 可以考英國公務員同考英軍咁，都係基於呢個原因。"},{"pid":"2e753e431d67b018580b6772051c9b45c14fc9ea","tid":1595661,"uid":120772,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:06:21.000Z","msg":"Working holiday 都可以做選民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86009173b5690bbcb5cc44b6b3a6b9c1110563e0","tid":1595661,"uid":27579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e753e431d67b018580b6772051c9b45c14fc9ea","tid":1595661,"uid":120772,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:06:21.000Z","msg":"Working holiday 都可以做選民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:08:17.000Z","msg":"如果你BN(O) 嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48fc940198fb68bb5dbb23f8920bbd117b34685a","tid":1595661,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc3c273e6d44f80f2169a753209187a221e7b25","tid":1595661,"uid":245198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:14:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3dcbb7beefcc2415e67d7af8c195d7e2d45fec66","tid":1595661,"uid":321846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86009173b5690bbcb5cc44b6b3a6b9c1110563e0","tid":1595661,"uid":27579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e753e431d67b018580b6772051c9b45c14fc9ea","tid":1595661,"uid":120772,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:06:21.000Z","msg":"Working holiday 都可以做選民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:08:17.000Z","msg":"如果你BN(O) 嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:21:38.000Z","msg":"或者英聯邦都可以<br />\n澳洲<br />\n紐西蘭<br />\n加拿大<br />\n<br />\n讀書 Spouse visa 都可以"},{"pid":"fb0b9459a9bc6b74cb9b28d93adeb79bde95f45e","tid":1595661,"uid":321846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e73461e43cb52d70f0f97c854f006535eb3e9ce1","tid":1595661,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:50:02.000Z","msg":"BNO 都得？<br />\n有冇source?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:23:51.000Z","msg":"樓上條英國政府官網 Link 有講！"},{"pid":"7363d6add7cd296f5f0d03b0181e0067004789c3","tid":1595661,"uid":27579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:54:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0201acdaf07a83ba35e0cbf88ae8f378d98f772e","tid":1595661,"uid":245198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef5fd879a29cf050de6e05941caf7d1fc40f0fcf","tid":1595661,"uid":245198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T10:33:58.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"03afbd7180572fbaf6c44e6725cc50f8bbc62476","tid":1595661,"uid":30209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7363d6add7cd296f5f0d03b0181e0067004789c3","tid":1595661,"uid":27579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:54:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T11:44:20.000Z","msg":"一定要幫巴打推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ag