lic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flennonway_public&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=be311b95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/lennonway_public</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Mwbs4U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Mwbs4U.jpg&h=2fc614dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9NhaJDh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9NhaJDh.jpg&h=a1b9bf55&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ra1ScwF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fra1ScwF.jpg&h=a2eadba0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oPGVUK2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoPGVUK2.jpg&h=969f75b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ad6KN44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAd6KN44.jpg&h=bb16e492&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee4f5b27ecbe2604cd32b232afcf7f027ade2e81","tid":1595661,"uid":245198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T09:08:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"581491fede001788e93b58e58d662ce44b22d498","tid":1595661,"uid":245198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00144f9b807f395b66068a9d88daf629b5e51217","tid":1595661,"uid":77224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f412bb4b5b472cd093300a4b5cc4616efccc1f3b","tid":1595661,"uid":27579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T07:16:43.000Z","msg":"【頭盔：幫fd 子post，我自己係英聯邦國籍都登記左了，大家唔好猶疑，登記左先！】 <br />\n<br />\n我哋係一群喺英國住咗幾年嘅香港人。<br />\n<br />\n我哋之前大家寫信畀各區國會議員，動之以情，但唔少回應都只係啲行貨。點解會咁？因為佢除咗普世價值之外，實在冇動力去幫香港人。<br />\n<br />\n我哋諗，點樣可以說之以利，令啲政界人物覺得幫我哋香港人唔單止係道理，亦都有佢着數？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">選票!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n英國今年內（11、12月）好大機會提前大選。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只要你現居英國，無論係英國公民、BNO、或英聯邦國家嘅國民，無論你持有咩visa都好，都可以登記做英國選民。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你即將過嚟讀書、working holiday，嚟緊九月尾/十月頭到埗，你應該趕得切登記做英國選民。<br />\n<br />\n如果你係英國公民，而又曾經喺英國住過，只要離英未夠15年，你可以登記喺海外郵寄投票。<br />\n<br />\n立即登記(只需要5分鐘): <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/register-to-vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fregister-to-vote&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=98ddd5dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/register-to-vote</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EJwR4cC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEJwR4cC.png&h=b90f8464&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KFRnrq1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKFRnrq1.png&h=b52b96d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋希望幫助所有合資格嘅香港手足，盡快登記做選民。其實登記咗唔單止可以幫香港，之後喺英國申請信用咭，呢邊啲銀行都係用選民登記冊做background check，所以絕對應該做，值得做，快啲做。<br />\n<br />\n差你一個，真係好多！！！！<br />\n<br />\n我哋分析過2017大選結果。英國選情仲激烈過香港區議會。<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">蘇格蘭NE Fife選區，即係 St Andrew's 大學所在地， 係2票定勝負！而最多香港人嘅倫敦，其中Imperial College所在嘅Kensington選區，工黨只係贏保守黨20票！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果遇上阻滯、遇上問題，請入嚟我哋嘅Telegram group：<a href=\"http://t.me/UKVoterAction4HK。我哋會盡力幫你解決。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUKVoterAction4HK%E3%80%82%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E6%9C%83%E7%9B%A1%E5%8A%9B%E5%B9%AB%E4%BD%A0%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E3%80%82&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=115eb14a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/UKVoterAction4HK。我哋會盡力幫你解決。</a><br />\n<br />\n未來行動：<br />\n● 我哋會整理英國各城市爭持激烈嘅選區(搖擺選區 / marginal seats)list。即將搬嚟英國，又未落戶嘅巴絲可以考慮下住係啲marginal seats，啲候選人會比較重視開拓新票源。<br />\n● 整電郵生成器，幫大家聯絡啲候選人；<br />\n● 喺啲香港同路人比較多，或者各黨爭持激烈嘅選區，組織大家約見候選人(面對面見，等佢哋有印象！佢哋競選都係要票，唔使怕醜)；<br />\n● 整理候選人對香港議題嘅立場/政綱，俾大家投票時參考。<br />\n<br />\n希望可以借助嚟緊選舉嘅契機，去engage呢邊嘅選舉政治，促使啲國會議員為香港發聲。<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<br />\nDemocracy for Hong Kong - Electoral Action Group 選舉行動組 (D4HK-EAG) <br />\n謹啟<br />\n<br />\nP.S.立即登記(只需要5分鐘): <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/register-to-vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fregister-to-vote&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=98ddd5dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/register-to-vote</a> <br />\n<br />\nP.P.S. D4HK Facebook 原post：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1572411313051960/posts/2152331705059915/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1572411313051960%2Fposts%2F2152331705059915%2F&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=798feeb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1572411313051960/posts/2152331705059915/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:37:11.000Z","msg":"幅圖要加返愛爾蘭(Republic of Ireland)<br />\n因歷史因素，愛爾蘭(Republic of Ireland)雖然唔係英聯邦國家，該國國民依然可以係英國投票"},{"pid":"1a56769c4da2c23840090c113248f8ad35f5d069","tid":1595661,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:38:54.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"65548b3b951db025b18ca8c4ce2d970cada1faa5","tid":1595661,"uid":245198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008dcb07f21e8afa6927c8c9c826ac0e525094f2","tid":1595661,"uid":245198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T00:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f33dd15d12f11904cde1d2b1a280132eed76210","tid":1595661,"uid":159417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T00:28:59.000Z","msg":"Push推 請聽君一言<br />\n麻煩手足暫時停止升級武力<br />\n文宣/輿論需要時間追上<br />\n(抗爭需要轉型,可持續發展)<br />\n要更多機會比和理非參與<br />\n達至全民一齊追求普世價值<br />\n<br />\n公平、自由、民主、公義、人權得來不易<br />\n漫長的道路上需要你支持我，我扶持你<br />\n有時惘然若失，但我們也要自信往前邁步<br />\n有咩嘢唔想失去，就努力捍衛同守護<br />\n現在就用自己雙手實踐夢想，迎接未來<br />\n<br />\n短期目標：改善抗爭能力，提升身份認同<br />\n建議：各有各做，best effort <br />\n中期目標：區議會(94%民主產生)<br />\n建議：關注身邊人，團結一致，各有各做<br />\n長期目標：強化民主陣營勢力<br />\n建議：抗爭生活化，減少比錢極權陣營<br />\n終極目標：民選議會、民選政府<br />\n建議：國際戰線、傳播思想、滲透內部<br />\n<br />\n公務員：小隱於野，中隱於市，大隱於朝<br />\n和勇合一：1.合法之下，最大勇武<br />\n2. 做任何事，永不被捕<br />\n<br />\n@謠言係疫症&bull;不傳播&bull;去求診&bull;澄清藥<br />\n@FakeNews係Cancer&bull;不擴散&bull;求事實&bull;割<br />\n@接觸資訊時，腦袋要清醒<br />\n<br />\n只要爭取民主團火未熄，還是有機會達成<br />\n衛城革命,生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡,打倒腐敗<br />\n@Template@<br />\n每日任務：0. 諗下做咩可以幫到手爭取民主1. 讀書、識法律2.運動、鬥長命3.幫襯良心商店、抵制送中商戶4.開AC玩國際戰線 (Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit)5.多發佈正面資訊、冷處理負面POST6.十點咆哮發泄7.思考完就take action<br />\n每星期任務：1. 低消費、高儲蓄、罷買日2. 教育家中兩老3. 去連儂牆幫手<br />\n每月任務：1. 換美金，走資2. 陪審員/派傳單/放映會/各有各做<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=319b3795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n理非可以做的事<a href=\"https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTakeActionWithYou&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=67f6ef8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou</a><br />\n良心與無良商戶<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=5e5771c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net</a><br />\n@Template@<br />\nVersion 2019.09.25"},{"pid":"b94edee17f1d3bdfaf0a97fbc907b55fa095733c","tid":1595661,"uid":120772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86009173b5690bbcb5cc44b6b3a6b9c1110563e0","tid":1595661,"uid":27579,"like":1